<section class="relative bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center py-20 lg:py-32 gap-12">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-center lg:text-left z-10">
        <span class="inline-block py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-700 font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Koleksi Terbaru</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-[1.1] mb-6">
          Melangkah Pasti dengan <span class="text-red-600">BALLQISH</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed">
          Sepatu pria kualitas terbaik dengan desain elegan dan material tahan lama. Nyaman dipakai untuk menemani aktivitas harian Anda.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <a href="#katalog" class="btn-primary">
            Lihat Katalog
          </a>
          <a href="#size-chart" class="btn-secondary">
            Panduan Ukuran
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595950653106-6c9ebd614d3a?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Sepatu Ballqish" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
